Printing Multivariate Outlier Detection

Source: R/print.multiOutliers.R
print.multiOutliers.Rd

Prints identified multivariate outliers

Usage

# S3 method for class 'multiOutliers'
print(x, ...)

Arguments

x

the results from "multiOutliers" function

...

not used

Value

A formatted print of the results of the "multiOutliers" function

Examples

#iForest
results <- multiOutliers(irisOutliers, method = "iforest")
results
